query:
SELECT 
  DATE_FORMAT(dr.date, '%Y-%m-%d') as date,
  b.nameAr as branch,
  dr.cashRevenue,
  dr.networkRevenue,
  dr.madaRevenue,
  dr.totalRevenue,
  dr.systemBalance,
  dr.notes
FROM daily_revenues dr
JOIN branches b ON dr.branchId = b.id
ORDER BY dr.date DESC
LIMIT 20;
